        <mxCell id="fr-content" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Users can create / open a document&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Multiple users edit the same document simultaneously&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Real-time broadcast of edits to all collaborators&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Rich-text formatting (bold, italic, headings, lists)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Document content persisted across sessions&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;- Export document as HTML file&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
