        <mxCell id="nfr-box" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- Low Latency: edit propagation &amp;lt; 200ms&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- High Availability: 99.9% uptime&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- Scalability: handle 100+ concurrent editors per doc&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- Consistency: eventual consistency for concurrent edits&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- Durability: document changes persisted to DB on every save&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;- Security: CORS controlled; session-based access per doc ID&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
